than a love letter to an Iraqi.

15:05.906 --> 15:08.157
It's a series of bunkers
outside Karbala, sir.

15:08.325 --> 15:10.493
- Maybe.
- Definitely, sir.

15:10.660 --> 15:12.369
The recon photos match.

15:12.662 --> 15:13.996
We'll see.

15:14.414 --> 15:16.123
Dag.

15:16.416 --> 15:19.335
It's what makes S.F. so badass.
We got the best flashlights.

15:19.920 --> 15:21.670
