No big deal.

16:09.344 --> 16:11.428
- What's the guy's name outside?
- Walter.

16:11.721 --> 16:14.890
- Bolo! Get in here!
- Who's Bolo, sir?

16:15.100 --> 16:17.059
Bolo is a guy who
doesn't know what he's doing.

16:17.227 --> 16:19.270
- Yes, sir?
- Want you to get this reporter...

16:19.437 --> 16:21.355
...off my back.
Know who Adriana Cruz is?

16:21.606 --> 16:23.399
- Reporter on NBS, sir.
- That's right.

16:23.608 --> 16:26.902
Tell her I'm checking a story
and you're bringing her to meet me.

16:27.112 --> 16:28.654
- In Iraq?
- No.

16:28.989 --> 16:31.365
I'll give you a fake copy of this map.

16:31.616 --> 16:33.659
Take her on a ride
that lasts all morning...

16:33.910 --> 16:36.662
